// SI ↔ SWAT unit/name conversion (legacy `konversi_si_swat`, parity G14). Used by
// the Phase-4 Excel weighing upload ("Upload Data Penimbangan") to translate the
// TPA desktop app's legacy naming (waste source, pool, unit) into SWAT entities,
// complementing `LegacyNameMap`. `category` scopes a mapping (WASTE_SOURCE | POOL
